  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.8.9">
<l>tuḷaṅku nīṇmuṭi yaracartaṅ kuricil toṇṭai maṉṉavaṉ tiṇṭiṟa loruvaṟ</l>
<l>kuḷaṅko ḷaṉpiṉō ṭiṉṉaruḷ curantaṅ kōṭu nāḻikai yēḻuṭa ṉiruppa</l>
<l>vaḷaṅkoḷ mantiram maṟṟavaṟ karuḷic ceyta vāṟaṭi yēṉaṟin tulakam</l>
<l>aḷanta poṉṉaṭi yēyaṭain tuyntē ṉaṇipo ḻiltiru varaṅkat tammāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I, [your] servant, knowing of the way you graciously bestowed</l>
<l rend="indent">the munificent mantra and more</l>
<l>To the chief of kings with tall, shining crowns, the king of Toṇṭai,</l>
<l rend="indent">the strong and brave one,</l>
<l>Lavishing your sweet grace with heart-filled love,</l>
<l rend="indent">when staying with [him] there continuously for seven nāḻikai,</l>
<l>Taking refuge at your golden feet which measured the world, [I] was saved,</l>
<l rend="indent">lord of sacred Araṅkam with lovely groves.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
